title: Grateful Dead Live at Autzen Stadium, U. of Oregon on 1994-06-18
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Sugaree, It's All Over Now, Tennessee Jed, Me & My Uncle*, Maggie's Farm, Candyman, Easy Answers

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Women Are Smarter-> Crazy Fingers-> Corinna-> Drums-> Space-> The Last Time, The Days Between-> One More Saturday Night, E: I Fought the Law

* Weir on acoustic guitar
